qir - A simple, effecent IRC client (under 2k LOC too!)
========================================================

qir (Quick IRc) is a simple, and cleanly written IRC 
client in C. It only has only one dependency, which is 
ncurses. It supports most irc features and runs on all 
unix-based operating systems (windows port on the way).

Installation
--------------
Installing qir is really simple, just open and modify 
config.mk as you see fit, then run these commands...

$ make
$ sudo make install

Usage
--------------
Run 'qir' and you're good to go!
For more help, run 'man qir' or
'qir -h'

